lemma untilI[intro]: fixes n assumes "\<exists>n''\<ge>n. \<gamma> t n'' \<and> (\<forall>n'\<ge>n. n'<n'' \<longrightarrow> \<gamma>' t n')" shows "(\<gamma>' \<UU>\<^sub>c \<gamma>) t n"
using assms until_def
by simp
